text: Fouad Mebazaa ( ; 15 June 1933 - 23 April 2025) was a Tunisian politician. He was the President of Tunisia from 15 January 2011 to 13 December 2011. Mebazaa died on 23 April 2025, at the age of 91. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1933 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Presidents of Tunisia Category:Prime Ministers of Tunisia Category:Speakers of the Assembly of the Representatives of the People
